    <node id="Facebook Advertising For Dummies">
      <data key="d0">Facebook Advertising For Dummies</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">"Facebook Advertising For Dummies" is a comprehensive guidebook published by Wiley Publishing, Inc., focusing on the intricacies of Facebook's advertising platform. Authored by Paul Dunay, Richard Krueger, and Joel Elad, the book offers detailed, step-by-step advice and real-world experiences to help readers master Facebook advertising. It covers a broad spectrum of topics crucial for effective advertising on the platform, including the creation of ad campaigns, precision ad targeting, optimizing landing pages, and testing and optimizing ads. The book is designed to enhance the marketing skills of its readers, enabling them to better engage with customers and sell products and services through Facebook.

The authors acknowledge the support of their families and the team at Wiley, including Amy Fandrei and Christopher Morris, who played significant roles in the book's development. Additionally, the book includes acknowledgments to numerous bloggers and Facebook's team for their contributions to the field of Facebook advertising. "Facebook Advertising For Dummies" is dedicated to advertisers navigating the significant changes in marketing history, emphasizing the use of Facebook as a platform for acquiring customers and selling products and services. The book is noted for its straightforward, step-by-step advice, making it a valuable resource for both novice and experienced advertisers looking to leverage Facebook's advertising capabilities.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9d0cbdc4ace277be49cf3080a2dd384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8be98569f399ade22c4128870942d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54c4f282202195546b69d41af58fab02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-383b51974a89cb1c06603ccf999e4d60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
