    <node id="Paul Dunay">
      <data key="d0">Paul Dunay</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Paul Dunay is an award-winning B2B marketing expert and author, best known for his significant contributions to the field of marketing and his authorship of books such as "Facebook Advertising For Dummies" and "Facebook Marketing For Dummies" published by Wiley. With over 20 years of experience, Dunay has specialized in generating demand and creating buzz for leading organizations across various sectors, including technology, consumer products, financial services, and professional services. He currently serves as the Global Managing Director of Services and Social Marketing for Avaya.

Dunay's innovative approach to integrated marketing has earned him numerous accolades. He was recognized as one of BtoB Magazine’s Top 25 B2B Marketers of the Year in 2009. Additionally, he won the DemandGen Award for Utilizing Marketing Automation to Fuel Corporate Growth in 2008. His excellence in marketing has also been acknowledged through multiple nominations and awards from the Information Technology Services Marketing Association (ITSMA), including being a five-time finalist in the Marketing Excellence Awards competition and a gold award winner in 2005.&lt;SEP&gt;Paul Dunay is one of the authors of the book Facebook Advertising For Dummies.&lt;SEP&gt;Paul Dunay is an award-winning B2B marketing expert with over 20 years of experience in generating demand and creating buzz for leading technology, consumer products, financial services, and professional services organizations. He is the Global Managing Director of Services and Social Marketing for Avaya and the author of Facebook Marketing For Dummies.&lt;SEP&gt;Paul Dunay is a marketing expert and author recognized among BtoB Magazine’s Top 25 BtoB Marketers of the Year in 2009.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
