    <node id="Richard Krueger">
      <data key="d0">Richard Krueger</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Richard Krueger is a prominent figure in the field of social media marketing, particularly known for his expertise in leveraging Facebook for business growth. He is one of the authors of the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," which underscores his authority in the domain of social media marketing. Richard is frequently quoted as an expert on social media marketing, reflecting his deep knowledge and influence in the industry.

In addition to his authorship, Richard Krueger is the co-founder and CEO of AboutFace Digital, a social media marketing agency that specializes in using Facebook as a platform for acquiring customers, building brands, and driving sales. His entrepreneurial spirit is evident through his extensive experience in various fields such as business development, branding, public relations, technical product development, and business management. Richard's successful track record includes leading business strategies for companies in diverse sectors including social media, interactive entertainment, broadband infrastructure, content syndication, mobile entertainment, online gaming, and local search. This comprehensive background highlights his versatility and expertise as a serial entrepreneur.&lt;SEP&gt;Richard Krueger is one of the authors of the book Facebook Advertising For Dummies.&lt;SEP&gt;Richard Krueger is the co-founder and CEO of AboutFace Digital, a social media marketing agency focused on using Facebook for acquiring customers, building brands, and driving sales. He is recognized as a serial entrepreneur with extensive experience in business development, branding, public relations, technical product development, and business management.&lt;SEP&gt;Richard Krueger is a frequently quoted authority on social media marketing.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
