    <node id="Joel Elad">
      <data key="d0">Joel Elad</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Joel Elad is an accomplished author and expert in online marketing, known for his significant contributions to literature on digital business and social media. He has authored several books, including "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," "LinkedIn For Dummies," "Starting an Online Business All-in-One For Dummies," and "Web Stores Do-It-Yourself For Dummies." With a total of six books on various online topics, Joel has established himself as a prominent figure in the field of digital marketing and entrepreneurship.

In addition to his writing career, Joel Elad is the head of Real Method Consulting, a company focused on educating people through various media such as training seminars, DVDs, and books. His educational background includes a Master’s Degree in Business from UC Irvine and a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science and Engineering from UCLA. Joel has also contributed to renowned publications like Entrepreneur magazine and Smartbiz.com, and has shared his expertise as an educator at institutions like the University of California, Irvine. His work and contributions have made him a respected authority in the realm of online business and marketing.&lt;SEP&gt;Joel Elad is one of the authors of the book Facebook Advertising For Dummies.&lt;SEP&gt;Joel Elad is an author who has written six books on various online topics, including LinkedIn For Dummies, Starting an Online Business All-in-One Desk Reference For Dummies, and Web Stores Do-It-Yourself For Dummies. He is the head of Real Method Consulting.&lt;SEP&gt;Joel Elad is an author known for books like LinkedIn For Dummies and coauthoring Starting an Online Business All-in-One For Dummies.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
