    <node id="Facebook">
      <data key="d0">Facebook</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Facebook is an online social network platform and company founded by Mark Zuckerberg, widely recognized as the most popular online social network on the planet. It is a significant focus of marketing strategies, particularly in the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies" authored by Paul Dunay, Richard Krueger, and Joel Elad. This book provides comprehensive guidance on advertising on Facebook, highlighting its capabilities for businesses to reach specific audiences based on demographics, interests, and geographic areas. Facebook is becoming the preferred platform for marketers and advertisers to acquire new customers, interact with existing ones, and sell products and services. The platform has undergone various changes in its advertising features, which are detailed in the book. Facebook offers robust advertising services and is central to modern advertising and marketing strategies. It is celebrated for rewriting the rules of marketing and is a pivotal tool for businesses aiming to enhance their marketing strategies through targeted advertising.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9d0cbdc4ace277be49cf3080a2dd384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8be98569f399ade22c4128870942d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54c4f282202195546b69d41af58fab02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-383b51974a89cb1c06603ccf999e4d60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
