    <node id="Cost Per Impression">
      <data key="d0">Cost Per Impression</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Cost Per Impression (CPM) is a pricing model where advertisers pay for every thousand times their ad is displayed, regardless of clicks.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost per impression is a pricing model in Facebook advertising where advertisers pay each time their ad is displayed.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost Per Impression (CPM) is a pricing model in Facebook advertising where advertisers pay for every thousand times their ad is displayed.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost Per Impression (CPM) is a pricing model where advertisers pay for every thousand times their ad is displayed.</data>
