    <node id="Wiley">
      <data key="d0">Wiley</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Wiley is a prominent publishing company known for its extensive involvement in producing and publishing educational and instructional books. Wiley is the publisher of the widely recognized "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," a book aimed at helping readers navigate the complexities of advertising on the Facebook platform. The company has a dedicated team of professionals who support authors throughout the writing and publishing process. Key team members involved in the production of these books include Amy Fandrei and Christopher Morris, among other editors and managers who play crucial roles in bringing these publications to market.

In addition to "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," Wiley has published several other books authored by notable writers such as Paul Dunay and Joel Elad. One such book is "Facebook Marketing For Dummies," which further underscores Wiley's commitment to providing comprehensive guides on social media marketing. Wiley is also the publisher behind the entire Dummies series, which is renowned for its user-friendly and accessible approach to a wide range of topics. This series includes various titles designed to simplify complex subjects for readers, making Wiley a trusted name in educational publishing.&lt;SEP&gt;Wiley is the publisher behind the book Facebook Advertising For Dummies.&lt;SEP&gt;Wiley is the publisher of the book, with a team including Amy Fandrei and Christopher Morris who supported the authors in writing and publishing the book.&lt;SEP&gt;Wiley is the publisher of the book Facebook Advertising For Dummies.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9d0cbdc4ace277be49cf3080a2dd384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8be98569f399ade22c4128870942d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54c4f282202195546b69d41af58fab02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-383b51974a89cb1c06603ccf999e4d60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
      <data key="d4">document_upload</data>
      <data key="d5">1773681444</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Amy Fandrei">
      <data key="d0">Amy Fandrei</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Amy Fandrei is an Acquisitions Editor at Wiley who played a crucial role in the development and publication of the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies." She initially reached out to the authors due to their insightful blogs and provided continuous support throughout the entire book writing and publishing process. Amy Fandrei was instrumental in bringing the book to market, showcasing her significant involvement in the project's success. Her role as an Acquisitions Editor highlights her expertise in identifying potential authors and guiding them through the complexities of the publishing process.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9d0cbdc4ace277be49cf3080a2dd384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8be98569f399ade22c4128870942d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54c4f282202195546b69d41af58fab02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-383b51974a89cb1c06603ccf999e4d60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
      <data key="d4">document_upload</data>
      <data key="d5">1773681456</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Christopher Morris">
      <data key="d0">Christopher Morris</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Christopher Morris is the Senior Project Editor at Wiley, where he played a pivotal role in the production and market release of the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies." In his capacity, he was instrumental in ensuring that the book adhered to the established For Dummies standards, a series known for its distinctive approach to instructional content. Christopher Morris was also responsible for keeping the authors on track throughout the writing and editing process, ensuring that the project timeline and quality benchmarks were met. His contributions were crucial in conforming the book to the specific stylistic and structural guidelines that define the For Dummies series, thereby maintaining consistency and quality across the publication.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d05f11d8cd14cec626dc00a88e73691&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9d0cbdc4ace277be49cf3080a2dd384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8be98569f399ade22c4128870942d41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54c4f282202195546b69d41af58fab02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36ea2f1d18a3512715c68e0a9de622cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-383b51974a89cb1c06603ccf999e4d60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284</data>
