      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">AboutFace Digital is a social media marketing agency co-founded by Richard Krueger, focusing on using Facebook for customer acquisition, brand building, and driving sales.&lt;SEP&gt;AboutFace Digital is a social media marketing agency focused on Facebook, co-founded by Richard Krueger. The agency specializes in acquiring customers, building brands, and driving sales.&lt;SEP&gt;AboutFace Digital is a social media marketing agency co-founded by Richard Krueger, specializing in using Facebook as a network for acquiring customers, building brands, and driving sales.&lt;SEP&gt;AboutFace Digital is a social media marketing agency co-founded and led by Richard Krueger, specializing in using Facebook for customer acquisition, brand building, and sales.</data>
