    <edge source="Facebook Advertising For Dummies" target="Paul Dunay">
      <data key="d7">11.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Paul Dunay is an author of the book *Facebook Advertising For Dummies*. He is recognized as a co-author of this work, where he contributed his expertise in marketing. The book, aimed at providing guidance on Facebook advertising, benefits from Dunay's professional insights, making it a valuable resource for readers seeking to understand and utilize Facebook's advertising platform effectively. His involvement underscores the collaborative effort behind the book, which is designed to help users navigate the complexities of Facebook advertising with practical advice and strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;Paul Dunay is a co-author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies, contributing his marketing expertise.&lt;SEP&gt;Paul Dunay is an author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies.</data>
      <data key="d9">authorship,collaboration,creation,marketing expertise,publication</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99</data>
