      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="Facebook Advertising For Dummies" target="Richard Krueger">
      <data key="d7">11.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Richard Krueger is an author of the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies." He is recognized for his contributions to the field of social media marketing, particularly through his work on this book. Richard Krueger co-authored "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," providing valuable insights into the strategies and techniques involved in advertising on the Facebook platform. His role as a co-author highlights his expertise and collaborative efforts in creating a comprehensive guide for users looking to navigate and utilize Facebook's advertising tools effectively. The book serves as a resource for understanding the nuances of social media marketing, with Krueger's input being instrumental in its development.&lt;SEP&gt;Richard Krueger is a co-author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies, providing insights on social media marketing.&lt;SEP&gt;Richard Krueger is an author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies.</data>
      <data key="d9">authorship,collaboration,creation,publication,social media marketing</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-a58f50b501da287bc4b403803ab7a518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-465a6256be496e6cf5317771a4c00cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b65b02a710fcc57a15eb01cf22547964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896b5301419980e8b8b5873114a8d6aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4db1d957d48d5297acd3f268ecb4fbc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90ce2b413b6eafb4694468b9017ee7bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872943548b37a379f517694d8e83ad1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c90a25ee0921e00d427736850c32284&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46d3e24e52e96a9dd97627ecf4ee3ae9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d650c7052460784fa721c70251a4db99</data>
