    <edge source="Facebook Advertising For Dummies" target="Joel Elad">
      <data key="d7">11.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Joel Elad is an author of the book "Facebook Advertising For Dummies." He is recognized as a co-author of this publication, where he shares his extensive knowledge in online marketing and online business strategies. His contributions to the book reflect his expertise in these areas, providing readers with valuable insights and practical advice on leveraging Facebook for advertising purposes. Throughout the various descriptions, Joel Elad is consistently identified as a key author of "Facebook Advertising For Dummies," highlighting his significant role in the creation of this comprehensive guide.&lt;SEP&gt;Joel Elad is a co-author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies, sharing his knowledge on online business.&lt;SEP&gt;Joel Elad is an author of Facebook Advertising For Dummies.</data>
      <data key="d9">authorship,collaboration,creation,online business,online marketing,publication</data>
